        <briefdescription>
<para>Build protocol name from its ID. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Given a protocol ID, this macro builds the protocol name. This is done by concatenating the scmi_protocol_ construct with the given protocol ID.</para>
